</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_352" id="175r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_352_r2l1">Eraſem von wyſentaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_352_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Eraſem als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hab von <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> leẅt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_352_r2l3">Cappell etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch nehſt geant = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_352_r2l4">wurtt / daʒ wır darcʒu niht <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> könten . vns <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> . denn dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_352_r2l5"><expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> leẅt dıe dıe ſache berüret mıt <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan> benennet . des wır ın <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_352_r2l6"><expan>yecʒıg<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef noch niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> mugt Jr wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_352_r2l7">wır noch nıht darcʒu <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> können / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_352_line_1577279197734_2545">oder dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_352" id="175r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Erasem von Wysentaw</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Erasem, als ir uns aber
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hab von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> lewt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Cappell
                        etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        ewch nehst geanwurtt, daz wir darczu niht
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> könten, uns
                            <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> denn die <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        lewt, die die sache berüret, mit <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan> benennet, des
                        wir in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>yeczig<ex>en</ex></expan> brief noch niht
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> mugt ir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, daz wir noch niht darczu
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> können. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                        oder dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                            <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
